==配套设施==

“山岗”除了学生宿舍，还有三栋综合楼
*De Neve Commons，位于De Neve Plaza<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://housing.ucla.edu/student-housing/freshman-students/living-on-campus/de-neve-plaza|title=De Neve Plaza|accessdate=2016-03-12|author=|date=|publisher=UCLA Housing|archive-date=2019-06-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190603025921/https://housing.ucla.edu/student-housing/freshman-students/living-on-campus/de-neve-plaza|dead-url=no}}</ref>
*Covel Commons
*Carnesale Commons，2013年开放，是全美第一个“健康饮食主题”食堂Bruin Plate（熊盘子）的所在地。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.latimes.com/home/la-hm-college-amenities-20150718-story.html|title=Prepare to be shocked (and jealous!) at the way college students live today|accessdate=2016-03-12|author=|date=|publisher=LA Times|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108191035/https://www.latimes.com/home/la-hm-college-amenities-20150718-story.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

每一栋综合楼内都提供自助食堂、学习室、会议室、演示厅，并提供银行和邮政服务。

“山岗”拥有四座大型自助食堂、三个快餐食堂、一个专供夜宵的服务、一个兼学习与饮食为一身的多功能食堂，为学生提供饮食服务<ref name = "dining">{{Cite web|url=https://housing.ucla.edu/dining-services/facilities-services-academic-year|title=Dining Locations|accessdate=2016-03-12|author=|date=|publisher=UCLA Dining Services|archive-date=2019-06-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190603214438/https://housing.ucla.edu/dining-services/facilities-services-academic-year|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

